videos.description: Boston College uses great ball movement to get the ball to Ky Bowman, who nails a deep three to give Boston College its opening points.
videos.headline: Bowman knocks down a deep 3

videos.description:
Bowman breaks ankles and nails 3

Boston College's Ky Bowman puts Florida State's PJ Savoy on skates and hits the three at the top of the key.
videos.headline: Bowman breaks ankles and nails 3
